title: Lichen Structure
description: The image features a close-up view of lichen, showcasing its intricate, branching structure. The lichen appears in shades of green and is depicted on a textured surface, possibly bark. Surrounding the central image are illustrations of the same lichen, emphasizing its unique morphology.

title: Lichen on Tree Bark
description: An illustration showing a tree trunk with greenish lichen growing on it. A circular inset highlights a close-up view of the lichen, showcasing its intricate, leafy texture and bluish-green color.

title: Lichen Patterns on Rock
description: A close-up view of a textured surface covered with various patches of lichen. The lichen displays vibrant green hues alongside gray and brown areas, creating a striking contrast against the rocky background. The intricate patterns and colors highlight the natural beauty and diversity of lichen growth.

title: Lichen on Rocks
description: The image features a close-up view of rocks covered in vibrant green lichen. The lichen appears in various shapes and sizes, contrasting against the gray surface of the rocks. A circular inset highlights a specific area of the rocks, showcasing the intricate patterns and textures created by the lichen.
